531
00:26:50,660 --> 00:27:03,819
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da u toj konkretnoj situaciji jednostavno emocionalno me previše drmnulo da nisam mogao biti svijestan u glavi.

532
00:27:04,339 --> 00:27:13,400
[SPEAKER_00] Jel bih rekao za sebe da si debelo kožac ili da te stvari brzo dotaknu?

533
00:27:13,400 --> 00:27:18,119
[SPEAKER_00] Zapravo kad govorimo o komunikaciji,

534
00:27:18,119 --> 00:27:21,099
[SPEAKER_00] šta je u pozadine komunikacije?

535
00:27:21,099 --> 00:27:23,319
[SPEAKER_00] Pozadine komunikacije su odnosi, ili tako?

536
00:27:24,279 --> 00:27:26,680
[SPEAKER_01] Pa mislim, prijenos informacija, ajmo reći,

537
00:27:26,680 --> 00:27:30,440
[SPEAKER_01] ali na kraju ne možeš izbaciti odnose bez istoga nikada.

538
00:27:30,440 --> 00:27:32,680
[SPEAKER_00] Onda očito i prijenos osjećaja, ali?

539
00:27:32,680 --> 00:27:33,799
[SPEAKER_01] Do, pa do.

540
00:27:33,799 --> 00:27:38,500
[SPEAKER_01] Mislim, možda ne prijenos, ali definitivno utjecaj na nekakve osjećaje.

541
00:27:38,500 --> 00:27:41,180
[SPEAKER_01] Šta je bilo prije i šta je bilo sad.

542
00:27:41,180 --> 00:27:44,359
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto je pitam?

543
00:27:44,359 --> 00:27:46,259
[SPEAKER_00] Da li se smatraš debelo kožac?

544
00:27:46,259 --> 00:27:51,619
[SPEAKER_00] Jer ako smo spominjali iskrenost,

545
00:27:51,619 --> 00:27:54,180
[SPEAKER_00] iskrenost prema sebi,

546
00:27:54,279 --> 00:27:56,500
[SPEAKER_00] iskrenost nekako i prema drugome,

547
00:27:56,500 --> 00:27:58,099
[SPEAKER_00] onda očito ako si iskreni prema sebi.

548
00:27:58,099 --> 00:28:03,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da li ikada razmišljaš o tome kako izbalansirati tu iskrenost

549
00:28:03,000 --> 00:28:07,839
[SPEAKER_00] i ne dovesti tu iskrenost do naivnosti,

550
00:28:07,839 --> 00:28:11,720
[SPEAKER_00] gdje to možda tebi šteti,

551
00:28:11,720 --> 00:28:14,119
[SPEAKER_00] gdje si autodestruktivan?

552
00:28:14,119 --> 00:28:16,200
[SPEAKER_01] Kako misliš do naivnosti?

553
00:28:16,200 --> 00:28:23,579
[SPEAKER_00] U svakom odnosu, pogotovo u pozicijama gdje ima puno ljudi na jednom mjestu,

554
00:28:23,579 --> 00:28:27,339
[SPEAKER_00] poput firmi ili obitelji,

555
00:28:27,339 --> 00:28:30,299
[SPEAKER_00] veća prijateljska okupljenja i tak dalje,

556
00:28:30,299 --> 00:28:37,599
[SPEAKER_00] postoji, nažalost, nešto što se zove

557
00:28:37,599 --> 00:28:40,359
[SPEAKER_00] i politika ili politiziranje.

558
00:28:40,740 --> 00:28:49,240
[SPEAKER_00] I sad, vjerovatno kada bi bili potpuno iskreni i komunicirali sve svoje emocije,

559
00:28:49,240 --> 00:28:55,099
[SPEAKER_00] možda bi nekad ispali slabi, možda bi nekad rekli nešto što će štetiti nama,

560
00:28:55,099 --> 00:28:57,440
[SPEAKER_00] našim interesima i tako dalje,

561
00:28:59,039 --> 00:29:07,680
[SPEAKER_00] da li ti, ili ako to radiš, kako to radiš, kako balansiraš tu iskrenost da ona ne postane naivnost koja postaje autodestrukcija?

562
00:29:07,759 --> 00:29:16,359
[SPEAKER_01] Mislim, kužim šta pitaš, ali mi se teško staviti u tu situaciju,

563
00:29:16,359 --> 00:29:22,660
[SPEAKER_01] jer u biti ta neka iskrenost koja gori mi u biti da čujem sebe,

564
00:29:23,039 --> 00:29:25,380
[SPEAKER_01] kako se ošćam u tom trenutku i da to priznam,

565
00:29:25,380 --> 00:29:26,980
[SPEAKER_01] znači da to ne izbjegavam.

566
00:29:26,980 --> 00:29:29,640
[SPEAKER_01] A onda samim time moš birat,

567
00:29:29,640 --> 00:29:32,680
[SPEAKER_01] hoćeš li to reći na glas ili nećeš.

568
00:29:32,680 --> 00:29:34,980
[SPEAKER_01] Da je ti fleksibilnost nekako.

569
00:29:34,980 --> 00:29:36,279
[SPEAKER_01] Nije da ja sad,

570
00:29:36,279 --> 00:29:39,579
[SPEAKER_01] apsolutno nisam taj liko i sve što mu je sad,

571
00:29:39,579 --> 00:29:41,220
[SPEAKER_01] na umu mu je na drumu.

572
00:29:41,220 --> 00:29:43,700
[SPEAKER_01] Ima tu

573
00:29:43,700 --> 00:29:45,859
[SPEAKER_01] taktičnosti.

574
00:29:45,859 --> 00:29:47,980
[SPEAKER_01] A što ne moš sad doći,

575
00:29:47,980 --> 00:29:50,400
[SPEAKER_01] ne znam, ja sam sklon pretjerivanju,

576
00:29:50,400 --> 00:29:51,759
[SPEAKER_01] pa će se truditi, ne pretjerivati,

577
00:29:51,839 --> 00:29:54,440
[SPEAKER_01] ali tako inače napravim po antu.

578
00:29:54,440 --> 00:29:56,160
[SPEAKER_01] Ali ne znam,

579
00:29:56,160 --> 00:30:00,059
[SPEAKER_01] ak je neko prošao neku traumu,

580
00:30:00,059 --> 00:30:02,500
[SPEAKER_01] i sad prolazi nešto,

581
00:30:02,500 --> 00:30:05,299
[SPEAKER_01] sad malo se bezobrazno prema tebi odnosio.

582
00:30:05,299 --> 00:30:06,960
[SPEAKER_01] Počnu ti reći, na šta je,

583
00:30:06,960 --> 00:30:08,460
[SPEAKER_01] na šta malo si mi bezobrazan.

584
00:30:08,460 --> 00:30:12,660
[SPEAKER_01] Pa možda si mogo i preko toga preći.

585
00:30:12,660 --> 00:30:13,559
[SPEAKER_01] To je opet.

586
00:30:13,559 --> 00:30:15,220
[SPEAKER_01] Jedna stvar je bit,

587
00:30:15,220 --> 00:30:18,839
[SPEAKER_01] ono što sam u biti bio rekao na početku,

588
00:30:18,839 --> 00:30:20,519
[SPEAKER_01] mislim da je jako bitno,

589
00:30:20,640 --> 00:30:24,279
[SPEAKER_01] pola priča je iskrenost prema sebi,

590
00:30:24,279 --> 00:30:27,640
[SPEAKER_01] ali pola priča je bit otvoren za drugoga.

591
00:30:27,640 --> 00:30:29,019
[SPEAKER_01] Ne moraš ti drugoga razumiti.

592
00:30:29,019 --> 00:30:31,319
[SPEAKER_01] Pazi, budimo iskreni.

593
00:30:31,319 --> 00:30:33,339
[SPEAKER_01] Niko tebe ne može razumiti.

594
00:30:33,339 --> 00:30:35,180
[SPEAKER_01] Niko mene ne može razumiti.

595
00:30:36,180 --> 00:30:38,880
[SPEAKER_01] ti može bit otvoren za čud šta ja govorim.

596
00:30:38,880 --> 00:30:40,819
[SPEAKER_01] Može šta se stvarno meni dešava u glavi,

597
00:30:40,819 --> 00:30:41,779
[SPEAKER_01] šta ja prolazim,

598
00:30:41,779 --> 00:30:43,400
[SPEAKER_01] ili šta ti prolaziš,

599
00:30:43,400 --> 00:30:44,839
[SPEAKER_01] kad kaješ razumijem te,

600
00:30:44,839 --> 00:30:45,180
[SPEAKER_01] ono,

601
00:30:45,180 --> 00:30:46,400
[SPEAKER_01] aproksimiram,

602
00:30:46,400 --> 00:30:47,460
[SPEAKER_01] ja moraš znam od prilike,

603
00:30:47,460 --> 00:30:49,640
[SPEAKER_01] ali sa stvarno da te netko razumije,

604
00:30:49,640 --> 00:30:51,759
[SPEAKER_01] nemoguće.

605
00:30:52,319 --> 00:30:56,039
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da opet da pravam bit konkretan,

606
00:30:56,039 --> 00:30:57,279
[SPEAKER_01] da odgovorim na tvoje pitanje,

607
00:30:57,279 --> 00:30:57,460
[SPEAKER_01] ono,

608
00:30:57,460 --> 00:30:58,359
[SPEAKER_01] kako balansiram.

609
00:30:58,359 --> 00:31:01,420
[SPEAKER_01] Bitno je čut,

610
00:31:01,420 --> 00:31:02,539
[SPEAKER_01] ono,

611
00:31:02,539 --> 00:31:02,900
[SPEAKER_01] šta,

612
00:31:02,900 --> 00:31:06,079
[SPEAKER_01] šta tebi taj to unutani glas govori o tebi,

613
00:31:06,079 --> 00:31:07,079
[SPEAKER_01] ali s druge strane,

614
00:31:07,079 --> 00:31:08,039
[SPEAKER_01] i bit svjestan

615
00:31:08,039 --> 00:31:09,559
[SPEAKER_01] te druge osobe.

616
00:31:09,819 --> 00:31:10,599
[SPEAKER_01] Jer ako nisi,

617
00:31:10,599 --> 00:31:12,640
[SPEAKER_01] to prelazi u stvarno bez obrazluku

618
00:31:12,640 --> 00:31:13,359
[SPEAKER_01] i egoizam.

619
00:31:13,359 --> 00:31:13,779
[SPEAKER_01] Znači,

620
00:31:13,779 --> 00:31:14,680
[SPEAKER_01] briga me ko si ti,

621
00:31:14,680 --> 00:31:15,319
[SPEAKER_01] šta si ti,

622
00:31:15,319 --> 00:31:15,599
[SPEAKER_01] naš,

623
00:31:15,599 --> 00:31:15,819
[SPEAKER_01] ono,

624
00:31:15,819 --> 00:31:16,400
[SPEAKER_01] Vinko,

625
00:31:16,400 --> 00:31:16,960
[SPEAKER_01] meni je to,

626
00:31:16,960 --> 00:31:17,619
[SPEAKER_01] Vinko,

627
00:31:17,619 --> 00:31:18,039
[SPEAKER_01] ne znam,

628
00:31:18,039 --> 00:31:20,019
[SPEAKER_01] ja se osjećam da me ne vidiš,

629
00:31:20,019 --> 00:31:20,619
[SPEAKER_01] Vinko,

630
00:31:20,619 --> 00:31:20,960
[SPEAKER_01] ono,

631
00:31:20,960 --> 00:31:23,839
[SPEAKER_01] ja mislim da mi ne daš dovoljno pozornosti,

632
00:31:23,839 --> 00:31:25,240
[SPEAKER_01] ono će samo bit Vinko,

633
00:31:25,240 --> 00:31:25,559
[SPEAKER_01] Vinko,

634
00:31:25,559 --> 00:31:25,920
[SPEAKER_01] Vinko,

635
00:31:25,920 --> 00:31:26,160
[SPEAKER_01] naš,

636
00:31:26,160 --> 00:31:26,299
[SPEAKER_01] ono,

637
00:31:26,299 --> 00:31:28,400
[SPEAKER_01] niko ne pita šta je Vinko,

638
00:31:28,400 --> 00:31:29,240
[SPEAKER_01] i to opet se vraćamo,

639
00:31:29,240 --> 00:31:29,960
[SPEAKER_01] to više nije,

640
00:31:29,960 --> 00:31:31,140
[SPEAKER_01] sto posto,

641
00:31:31,140 --> 00:31:32,140
[SPEAKER_01] sto posto od nas,

642
00:31:32,380 --> 00:31:33,240
[SPEAKER_01] sto posto,

643
00:31:33,240 --> 00:31:33,599
[SPEAKER_01] a ti,

644
00:31:33,599 --> 00:31:34,539
[SPEAKER_01] briga me,

645
00:31:34,539 --> 00:31:35,200
[SPEAKER_01] koliko daješ,

646
00:31:35,200 --> 00:31:36,299
[SPEAKER_01] dao ti sto ili nula,

647
00:31:36,299 --> 00:31:39,079
[SPEAKER_01] ne zanima me.

648
00:31:39,079 --> 00:31:41,799
[SPEAKER_00] Po zapravo mislim da si tu pojentirao,

649
00:31:41,799 --> 00:31:42,079
[SPEAKER_00] mislim,

650
00:31:42,079 --> 00:31:43,619
[SPEAKER_00] bar mi iz moje perspektive,

651
00:31:43,619 --> 00:31:44,500
[SPEAKER_00] ja mislim,

652
00:31:44,500 --> 00:31:46,460
[SPEAKER_00] kakogod se mi trudili,

653
00:31:46,460 --> 00:31:47,099
[SPEAKER_00] znači,

654
00:31:47,099 --> 00:31:48,480
[SPEAKER_00] ja bih rekao,

655
00:31:48,480 --> 00:31:48,779
[SPEAKER_00] evo,

656
00:31:48,779 --> 00:31:51,599
[SPEAKER_00] sjedio sam na balkonu

657
00:31:51,599 --> 00:31:52,400
[SPEAKER_00] kod svojih staraca,

658
00:31:52,400 --> 00:31:53,880
[SPEAKER_00] sad ovaj vikend sam bio u Osijeku,

659
00:31:53,880 --> 00:31:55,220
[SPEAKER_00] i ona naš,

660
00:31:55,220 --> 00:31:55,819
[SPEAKER_00] dođeš tamo,

661
00:31:55,819 --> 00:31:56,839
[SPEAKER_00] roditelji ti stare,

662
00:31:56,839 --> 00:31:58,660
[SPEAKER_00] moja djeca rastu,

663
00:31:58,660 --> 00:32:01,259
[SPEAKER_00] gledam to okruženje tamo,

664
00:32:01,259 --> 00:32:02,019
[SPEAKER_00] gdje sam odrastao,

665
00:32:02,099 --> 00:32:02,779
[SPEAKER_00] to dvorište,

666
00:32:02,779 --> 00:32:06,059
[SPEAKER_00] i onda mi je

667
00:32:06,059 --> 00:32:07,339
[SPEAKER_00] samo onak sinulo,

668
00:32:07,339 --> 00:32:08,680
[SPEAKER_00] i nekako mi je bilo poizdano

669
00:32:08,680 --> 00:32:10,059
[SPEAKER_00] svojim našim današnjim razgovorom,

670
00:32:10,059 --> 00:32:12,039
[SPEAKER_00] stvarno,

671
00:32:12,039 --> 00:32:13,660
[SPEAKER_00] bar mi iz moje perspektive,

672
00:32:13,660 --> 00:32:16,240
[SPEAKER_00] cijeli život može svesti na odnose,

673
00:32:16,240 --> 00:32:17,279
[SPEAKER_00] i na druge ljude.

674
00:32:17,279 --> 00:32:20,259
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, imaš odnos sa samim sobom,

675
00:32:20,259 --> 00:32:21,319
[SPEAKER_00] imaš odnos sa druge ljude.

676
00:32:21,319 --> 00:32:22,119
[SPEAKER_01] Da, da, mislim da je to bitno.

677
00:32:22,119 --> 00:32:26,059
[SPEAKER_00] Bilo, radilo se o tvojoj prvoj obitelji,

678
00:32:26,059 --> 00:32:27,039
[SPEAKER_00] pa tvojoj drugoj obitelji,

679
00:32:27,039 --> 00:32:27,680
[SPEAKER_00] tvoje djeci,

680
00:32:27,680 --> 00:32:29,859
[SPEAKER_00] tvojim prijateljima,

681
00:32:29,859 --> 00:32:31,720
[SPEAKER_00] tvojim poslovnim kolegama,

682
00:32:31,819 --> 00:32:33,839
[SPEAKER_00] ženi, mužu, što god,

683
00:32:33,839 --> 00:32:35,160
[SPEAKER_00] partnerima,

684
00:32:35,160 --> 00:32:37,519
[SPEAKER_00] sve se svede na kraju na to,

685
00:32:37,519 --> 00:32:39,160
[SPEAKER_00] i na dinamiku tih odnosa.

686
00:32:39,160 --> 00:32:41,519
[SPEAKER_00] I meni je fascinantno da,

687
00:32:41,519 --> 00:32:44,819
[SPEAKER_00] ako je to činjenica,

688
00:32:44,819 --> 00:32:47,039
[SPEAKER_00] meni je fascinantno koliko smo mi

689
00:32:47,039 --> 00:32:48,420
[SPEAKER_00] nevješti,

690
00:32:48,420 --> 00:32:50,579
[SPEAKER_00] i loši u tome.

691
00:32:52,259 --> 00:32:54,259
[SPEAKER_00] čak i oni koji se trude

692
00:32:54,259 --> 00:32:55,279
[SPEAKER_00] postati bolji,

693
00:32:55,279 --> 00:32:59,980
[SPEAKER_00] ja nekad imam osjećaj da što više sam se trudio,

694
00:32:59,980 --> 00:33:02,160
[SPEAKER_00] što više sam učio o tome da sam sve glopljiv i glopljiv.

695
00:33:02,160 --> 00:33:02,900
[SPEAKER_01] Da, da, da.

696
00:33:02,900 --> 00:33:05,299
[SPEAKER_00] I da možda imaš i čak i previše informacija

697
00:33:05,299 --> 00:33:07,579
[SPEAKER_00] i onda ti stvore možda

698
00:33:07,579 --> 00:33:09,180
[SPEAKER_00] nepotreban šum uopće

699
00:33:09,180 --> 00:33:12,640
[SPEAKER_00] i izgubiš tu nekakvu jednostavnost

700
00:33:12,640 --> 00:33:14,500
[SPEAKER_00] i lakoću.

701
00:33:14,500 --> 00:33:15,759
[SPEAKER_01] Pa, apsolutno, ima.

702
00:33:15,759 --> 00:33:17,200
[SPEAKER_00] Možda nisi u trenutku,

703
00:33:17,200 --> 00:33:18,660
[SPEAKER_00] možda previše kalibriraš

704
00:33:18,660 --> 00:33:20,099
[SPEAKER_00] kao neki socijalni kalkulator.

705
00:33:20,099 --> 00:33:20,880
[SPEAKER_01] Da, da, da.

706
00:33:20,880 --> 00:33:21,220
[SPEAKER_00] Jel?

707
00:33:21,220 --> 00:33:23,460
[SPEAKER_01] Da, da, ima, ima, apsolutno.

708
00:33:23,460 --> 00:33:27,000
[SPEAKER_01] U svemu ima pretjerivanja,

709
00:33:27,000 --> 00:33:28,940
[SPEAKER_01] ali da, da misli da je bitno ovo što si rekao,

710
00:33:28,940 --> 00:33:30,359
[SPEAKER_01] baš nekako rezoniran s time,

711
00:33:30,359 --> 00:33:31,779
[SPEAKER_01] da odnosi,

712
00:33:31,779 --> 00:33:35,099
[SPEAKER_01] ali odnosi prema tebi je isto ono,

713
00:33:35,099 --> 00:33:36,839
[SPEAKER_01] sam prema sebi je isto nekakav ono

714
00:33:36,839 --> 00:33:38,460
[SPEAKER_01] odnos koji treba njegovat,

715
00:33:38,460 --> 00:33:39,440
[SPEAKER_01] u principu.

716
00:33:39,440 --> 00:33:42,279
[SPEAKER_01] I meni je trebalo dugo da skužim

717
00:33:42,279 --> 00:33:42,759
[SPEAKER_01] taj dio.

718
00:33:42,759 --> 00:33:44,400
[SPEAKER_01] Baš mi je dugo trebalo, evo.

719
00:33:44,400 --> 00:33:45,960
[SPEAKER_00] Ne znam, ne znam zašto,

720
00:33:45,960 --> 00:33:46,740
[SPEAKER_00] ali sad imamo osjeća

721
00:33:46,740 --> 00:33:47,359
[SPEAKER_00] kao da smo neke,

722
00:33:47,359 --> 00:33:48,680
[SPEAKER_00] kao neke dvije tetke na kavi,

723
00:33:48,680 --> 00:33:48,859
[SPEAKER_00] ono.

724
00:33:48,859 --> 00:33:53,740
[SPEAKER_00] Jel' ovo preintimno o čem mi pričamo sada?

725
00:33:53,740 --> 00:33:56,579
[SPEAKER_01] A, misli, muši smo u neke intimne teme.

726
00:33:56,579 --> 00:33:58,339
[SPEAKER_00] Jel' ovako dva muškarce,

727
00:33:58,339 --> 00:33:59,119
[SPEAKER_00] ovaj kao ja i ti,

728
00:33:59,119 --> 00:34:01,799
[SPEAKER_00] trebaju javno pričati o ovakvim stvarima

729
00:34:01,799 --> 00:34:04,359
[SPEAKER_00] ili uopće privatno razmišljati o ovakvim stvarima?

730
00:34:04,359 --> 00:34:05,880
[SPEAKER_01] Pa, privatno.

731
00:34:05,880 --> 00:34:06,759
[SPEAKER_00] Jel' to ovaj,

