00:39:42,099 --> 00:39:43,599
[SPEAKER_00] ne zna postavi granicu,

951
00:39:43,599 --> 00:39:44,460
[SPEAKER_00] kako treba.

952
00:39:44,460 --> 00:39:45,880
[SPEAKER_01] A možda da,

953
00:39:45,880 --> 00:39:48,059
[SPEAKER_01] sve to agreeable.

954
00:39:48,059 --> 00:39:49,239
[SPEAKER_01] Agreeable, da.

955
00:39:49,239 --> 00:39:54,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da više nemamo dobar ekvivalent tamo.

956
00:39:54,000 --> 00:39:55,780
[SPEAKER_00] Možda ima da se mi ne možemo osjetiti.

957
00:39:55,780 --> 00:39:56,380
[SPEAKER_01] Možda ima, da.

958
00:39:56,380 --> 00:40:00,099
[SPEAKER_01] Ali mislim da bi nekako naj...

959
00:40:00,099 --> 00:40:01,900
[SPEAKER_00] I što bi bila suprotnost uopće?

960
00:40:02,179 --> 00:40:04,679
[SPEAKER_00] toj karakteristiki,

961
00:40:04,679 --> 00:40:06,159
[SPEAKER_00] karakteristici?

962
00:40:06,159 --> 00:40:08,420
[SPEAKER_00] Što bi bilo suprotno?

963
00:40:08,420 --> 00:40:09,000
[SPEAKER_00] Direktan?

964
00:40:09,000 --> 00:40:12,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ili netko ko...

965
00:40:12,000 --> 00:40:14,079
[SPEAKER_01] Pa znači, ako razmišljam kao...

966
00:40:14,079 --> 00:40:15,280
[SPEAKER_00] Hoći netko prihvaćan?

967
00:40:15,280 --> 00:40:16,179
[SPEAKER_00] Da.

968
00:40:16,179 --> 00:40:19,280
[SPEAKER_00] Hoćeš li ići sa mnom na piće?

969
00:40:19,280 --> 00:40:19,820
[SPEAKER_00] Može.

970
00:40:19,820 --> 00:40:23,360
[SPEAKER_00] Hoćeš li mi pomoć urediti studio?

971
00:40:23,360 --> 00:40:24,159
[SPEAKER_00] Hoću.

972
00:40:24,159 --> 00:40:25,599
[SPEAKER_00] Hoćeš li...

973
00:40:25,599 --> 00:40:26,860
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, što god te neko pita,

974
00:40:26,860 --> 00:40:27,480
[SPEAKER_00] ti pristaneš.

975
00:40:27,480 --> 00:40:27,900
[SPEAKER_01] Da, da.

976
00:40:27,900 --> 00:40:30,059
[SPEAKER_00] To bi trebala biti ta osoba.

977
00:40:30,059 --> 00:40:31,480
[SPEAKER_01] Da, Agreeable kao koja.

978
00:40:31,539 --> 00:40:32,639
[SPEAKER_01] Da, ko prihvaća.

979
00:40:32,639 --> 00:40:34,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ko kaže na sve.

980
00:40:34,000 --> 00:40:35,159
[SPEAKER_01] Svi prihvaća.

981
00:40:35,159 --> 00:40:35,579
[SPEAKER_01] Da, sve može.

982
00:40:35,579 --> 00:40:37,300
[SPEAKER_01] U biti, možda više...

983
00:40:37,300 --> 00:40:41,400
[SPEAKER_01] Možda nije nužno kontekst u prihvaćanju,

984
00:40:41,400 --> 00:40:44,519
[SPEAKER_01] nego prihvaća mimo sebe.

985
00:40:44,519 --> 00:40:47,480
[SPEAKER_01] Što nema ništa lošo u tome da ti neko kažeš,

986
00:40:47,480 --> 00:40:48,480
[SPEAKER_01] nešto ti kažeš da.

987
00:40:48,480 --> 00:40:52,519
[SPEAKER_01] Možda si više Agreeable u tom kontekstu,

988
00:40:52,519 --> 00:40:56,519
[SPEAKER_01] ako kažeš da i na stvari na koje možda ne bih htio reći da.

989
00:40:58,219 --> 00:40:59,639
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, ja mislim da nemam ništa...

990
00:40:59,639 --> 00:41:00,840
[SPEAKER_01] Što, šit samo na piće?

991
00:41:00,840 --> 00:41:01,760
[SPEAKER_01] Ako ja želim, da.

992
00:41:01,760 --> 00:41:03,099
[SPEAKER_01] Da li me to čini Agreeable?

993
00:41:03,099 --> 00:41:05,380
[SPEAKER_01] Ne, ja želim ić s tobom na piće.

994
00:41:05,380 --> 00:41:07,639
[SPEAKER_01] Činilo bi me ako ona...

995
00:41:07,639 --> 00:41:08,900
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, možda bih htio reći,

996
00:41:08,900 --> 00:41:10,300
[SPEAKER_01] je li ti, ili mi ti kažeš svoje mišlje?

997
00:41:10,380 --> 00:41:11,860
[SPEAKER_01] A, Slaveno, ja mislim da si ti glup.

998
00:41:11,860 --> 00:41:13,059
[SPEAKER_01] A da, da, je.

999
00:41:13,059 --> 00:41:15,880
[SPEAKER_01] Mislim, to jednu ruku isto Agreeable,

1000
00:41:15,880 --> 00:41:18,539
[SPEAKER_01] nemam nikako ništa da vratim,

1001
00:41:18,539 --> 00:41:20,940
[SPEAKER_01] nemam mišljenja o tome,

1002
00:41:20,940 --> 00:41:24,019
[SPEAKER_01] nego samo slijedim ono što mi neko drugi govori.

1003
00:41:24,019 --> 00:41:27,539
[SPEAKER_00] Da li misliš da je ta karakteristika,

1004
00:41:27,539 --> 00:41:31,239
[SPEAKER_00] recimo osobe koje prihvaća čak i ono što nije,

1005
00:41:31,239 --> 00:41:35,659
[SPEAKER_00] u skladu sa onim što on želi, recimo,

1006
00:41:35,659 --> 00:41:37,619
[SPEAKER_00] i s njegovim stavima, uvjerenjima i tako dalje.

1007
00:41:37,619 --> 00:41:40,639
[SPEAKER_00] Da li je to na nekakav način isto i pitanje toga

1008
00:41:40,639 --> 00:41:41,880
[SPEAKER_00] da se ne poznaje dovoljno,

1009
00:41:41,880 --> 00:41:44,840
[SPEAKER_00] ili da fali vodlučnosti,

1010
00:41:44,840 --> 00:41:46,840
[SPEAKER_00] ili da fali samopouzdanje?

1011
00:41:46,840 --> 00:41:49,199
[SPEAKER_00] Hrabrosti.

1012
00:41:49,199 --> 00:41:50,300
[SPEAKER_00] Hrabrosti?

1013
00:41:50,300 --> 00:41:53,079
[SPEAKER_01] Da, mislim da...

1014
00:41:53,079 --> 00:41:54,400
[SPEAKER_00] Ali strah čega onda?

1015
00:41:54,400 --> 00:41:57,980
[SPEAKER_00] Strah povrđivanja te druge osobe ili nešto?

1016
00:41:57,980 --> 00:41:59,699
[SPEAKER_01] Pa može biti,

1017
00:42:00,079 --> 00:42:02,880
[SPEAKER_01] To je uvratno dio nekakvog odrastanja ili traume

1018
00:42:02,880 --> 00:42:07,079
[SPEAKER_01] ili, ne znam, jednostavno kako te okolina oblikovala,

1019
00:42:07,079 --> 00:42:12,119
[SPEAKER_01] pa zato te strah vjerovat sebi i slušat sebe

1020
00:42:12,119 --> 00:42:15,579
[SPEAKER_01] možda kroz djetinstvo, kroz školu,

1021
00:42:15,579 --> 00:42:17,440
[SPEAKER_01] kroz srednju, kroz fakultet.

1022
00:42:17,440 --> 00:42:21,139
[SPEAKER_01] Si bio kažnjan za to što si ti bio svoj

1023
00:42:21,139 --> 00:42:22,500
[SPEAKER_01] ili nisi bio prihvaćan.

1024
00:42:22,500 --> 00:42:25,159
[SPEAKER_01] I on si se naučio adaptirati u principu da

1025
00:42:25,159 --> 00:42:28,920
[SPEAKER_01] neću ja biti ja, nego ću ja prihvati što drugi misle

1026
00:42:28,920 --> 00:42:31,960
[SPEAKER_01] ili što drugi govore i što drugi mi kažu da treba napreti,

1027
00:42:31,960 --> 00:42:33,019
[SPEAKER_01] onda ću biti prihvaćen.

1028
00:42:33,019 --> 00:42:40,059
[SPEAKER_01] I mislim da puno hrabrosti tu treba imat kad dolaziš iz takvog mindseta,

1029
00:42:40,059 --> 00:42:42,199
[SPEAKER_01] gdje ti, isto koje na počešku smo pričali,

1030
00:42:42,199 --> 00:42:43,860
[SPEAKER_01] gdje ti osjetiš to.

1031
00:42:43,860 --> 00:42:46,440
[SPEAKER_01] Ti osjetiš potencijalno odbijanje,

1032
00:42:46,440 --> 00:42:48,820
[SPEAKER_01] ti osjetiš da ti nećeš bit dio,

1033
00:42:48,820 --> 00:42:51,219
[SPEAKER_01] ne znam, nekakvog kolektiva,

1034
00:42:51,320 --> 00:42:53,539
[SPEAKER_01] da nećeš biti shvaćen, da nećeš biti vidjen.

1035
00:42:53,539 --> 00:42:55,039
[SPEAKER_01] Ti to osjetiš.

1036
00:42:55,039 --> 00:42:58,780
[SPEAKER_01] I sad, biti hrabar, poslušat sebe i reći ne,

1037
00:42:58,780 --> 00:43:01,099
[SPEAKER_01] i riskirat biti odbačen od toga.

1038
00:43:01,099 --> 00:43:02,280
[SPEAKER_01] To je ono,

1039
00:43:02,280 --> 00:43:03,960
[SPEAKER_01] velika stvar.

1040
00:43:04,360 --> 00:43:07,440
[SPEAKER_00] Ja mogu zapravo dat nekako na svom primjeru,

1041
00:43:07,440 --> 00:43:10,340
[SPEAKER_00] znaš da sam bio u jednoj dugačkoj vezi.

1042
00:43:10,340 --> 00:43:10,940
[SPEAKER_01] Da.

1043
00:43:10,940 --> 00:43:16,599
[SPEAKER_00] I zapravo sam shvatio te kad sam izašao iz te veze,

1044
00:43:16,599 --> 00:43:18,400
[SPEAKER_00] kad sam bio nekoliko godina sam,

1045
00:43:18,400 --> 00:43:22,280
[SPEAKER_00] i ta veza je dosta dugo trala,

1046
00:43:22,280 --> 00:43:23,860
[SPEAKER_00] znači ja sam prekring,

1047
00:43:23,860 --> 00:43:27,260
[SPEAKER_00] izašao sam iz te veze sa 30-ta godina,

1048
00:43:27,260 --> 00:43:28,719
[SPEAKER_00] tako nešto rane, 30-te,

1049
00:43:28,719 --> 00:43:31,559
[SPEAKER_00] i ja sam skušao da sam cijele 20-te proveo u vezi,

1050
00:43:31,559 --> 00:43:33,659
[SPEAKER_00] da ja zapravo uopće nisam znao što ja želim.

1051
00:43:34,280 --> 00:43:36,760
[SPEAKER_00] Da sam jako puno kompromisa radio,

1052
00:43:36,760 --> 00:43:38,500
[SPEAKER_00] možda sam i previše prihvaćao,

1053
00:43:38,500 --> 00:43:41,079
[SPEAKER_00] recimo ideje ili ono,

1054
00:43:41,079 --> 00:43:42,659
[SPEAKER_00] što god, odluke te druge osobe,

1055
00:43:42,659 --> 00:43:43,920
[SPEAKER_00] onako se priklanja,

1056
00:43:43,920 --> 00:43:47,119
[SPEAKER_00] možda išao linijom manjeg odpora ili što god.

1057
00:43:47,119 --> 00:43:50,360
[SPEAKER_00] I onda sam se našao ono na nekoj vjetrometini,

1058
00:43:50,360 --> 00:43:52,400
[SPEAKER_00] onako da sam skužio kao, što ja želim?

1059
00:43:52,400 --> 00:43:53,420
[SPEAKER_01] Tko sam ja.

1060
00:43:53,420 --> 00:43:54,219
[SPEAKER_00] Tko sam ja.

1061
00:43:54,219 --> 00:43:58,679
[SPEAKER_00] Sada ne idemo na one do ne najdublje razine duhovne,

1062
00:43:58,679 --> 00:43:59,800
[SPEAKER_00] i tako dalje.

1063
00:43:59,800 --> 00:44:02,079
[SPEAKER_00] Filozofski skroz kao tko sam ja,

1064
00:44:02,079 --> 00:44:04,260
[SPEAKER_00] nego na ovaj nekoj svijetom,

1065
00:44:04,260 --> 00:44:05,320
[SPEAKER_00] na razine tko sam ja,

1066
00:44:05,320 --> 00:44:06,280
[SPEAKER_00] koji su moji interesi,

1067
00:44:06,280 --> 00:44:06,960
[SPEAKER_00] što ja želim,

1068
00:44:06,960 --> 00:44:08,039
[SPEAKER_00] da li bi ovo me rekao da,

1069
00:44:08,039 --> 00:44:09,079
[SPEAKER_00] ili bi ovo me rekao ne.

1070
00:44:09,079 --> 00:44:12,480
[SPEAKER_00] Imaš nekako bolju mogućnost,

1071
00:44:12,480 --> 00:44:14,519
[SPEAKER_00] jasnije to vidjeti kad si sam,

1072
00:44:14,519 --> 00:44:15,760
[SPEAKER_00] kad nisi s nekim u vesijem.

1073
00:44:15,760 --> 00:44:17,820
[SPEAKER_01] I kad si izvam toga odjednom.

1074
00:44:17,820 --> 00:44:28,659
[SPEAKER_00] i ovaj, zapravo onda očito polaziš na točka toga da ne prihvaćaš stalno,

1075
00:44:28,659 --> 00:44:32,960
[SPEAKER_00] nego da možeš biti odlučan, da možeš biti okej i hrabar.

1076
00:44:32,960 --> 00:44:36,300
[SPEAKER_00] Mislim, kako ćeš biti hrabar, uopće ako ne znaš šta želiš.

1077
00:44:37,940 --> 00:44:40,440
[SPEAKER_00] Uglavnom su ti ljudi koji prihvaćaju sve,

1078
00:44:40,440 --> 00:44:41,519
[SPEAKER_00] oni ne znaju tko su oni,

1079
00:44:41,519 --> 00:44:42,780
[SPEAKER_00] po mojom mišljenju.

1080
00:44:43,320 --> 00:44:44,639
[SPEAKER_00] I njima je sve okej.

1081
00:44:44,639 --> 00:44:46,059
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, idemo na Tajland.

1082
00:44:46,059 --> 00:44:46,880
[SPEAKER_00] Ajmo na Tajland.

1083
00:44:46,880 --> 00:44:48,380
[SPEAKER_00] Ajmo...

1084
00:44:48,380 --> 00:44:49,619
[SPEAKER_00] Ja čak mislim suprotno.

1085
00:44:49,619 --> 00:44:50,360
[SPEAKER_00] Ajde, suprotno.

1086
00:44:50,360 --> 00:44:50,760
[SPEAKER_01] Ozmijeno.

1087
00:44:50,760 --> 00:44:52,760
[SPEAKER_01] Ja mislim da...

1088
00:44:52,760 --> 00:44:56,420
[SPEAKER_01] Opet, znači, možda je to abstraktno,

1089
00:44:56,420 --> 00:44:57,739
[SPEAKER_01] ali to je bio moj nekakav put.

1090
00:44:57,739 --> 00:45:02,519
[SPEAKER_01] Ja mislim da svi mi znamo manje više tko smo,

1091
00:45:02,519 --> 00:45:04,820
[SPEAKER_01] ili te neke osnovne stvari koje su nam bitne.

1092
00:45:04,820 --> 00:45:07,260
[SPEAKER_01] I kad dođeš u situaciju da kažeš da,

1093
00:45:07,260 --> 00:45:08,639
[SPEAKER_01] a da ne želiš reći da,

1094
00:45:08,639 --> 00:45:10,340
[SPEAKER_01] ja mislim da se svjestom toga.

1095
00:45:10,340 --> 00:45:12,119
[SPEAKER_00] Ali osjećaš možda tek nakon?

1096
00:45:13,320 --> 00:45:14,019
[SPEAKER_01] Da, da.

1097
00:45:14,019 --> 00:45:16,280
[SPEAKER_01] Mislim, moguće je da osjetiš ti to i...

1098
00:45:16,280 --> 00:45:19,019
[SPEAKER_01] Čak i osjetiš i tad ja i ovom primjeru

1099
00:45:19,019 --> 00:45:21,599
[SPEAKER_01] što sam dao kad sam pustio ovome da...

1100
00:45:21,599 --> 00:45:22,599
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam osjetio to.

1101
00:45:22,599 --> 00:45:24,380
[SPEAKER_01] Ja nisam mogo prepoznat,

1102
00:45:24,380 --> 00:45:27,380
[SPEAKER_01] nisam bio uviđavan toliko da skužim

1103
00:45:27,380 --> 00:45:29,960
[SPEAKER_01] koja je to emocija, odakle ona dolazi.

1104
00:45:29,960 --> 00:45:31,860
[SPEAKER_01] To možda nešto što treba vježbat.

1105
00:45:31,860 --> 00:45:34,840
[SPEAKER_01] Ali znaš, ako ćemo pojednostavni stvari,

1106
00:45:34,840 --> 00:45:37,360
[SPEAKER_01] u nekom trenu, ako te neko pita

1107
00:45:37,360 --> 00:45:38,219
[SPEAKER_01] hoćeš li s nama,

1108
00:45:38,219 --> 00:45:41,619
[SPEAKER_01] ja mislim da ti imaš vrlo jasan

1109
00:45:41,619 --> 00:45:43,599
[SPEAKER_01] unutarnji osjećaj želim ili ne želim.

1110
00:45:43,599 --> 00:45:46,760
[SPEAKER_01] Sad, možda ga ne znaš opisat

1111
00:45:46,760 --> 00:45:48,960
[SPEAKER_01] zašto želim ili zašto ne želim,

1112
00:45:48,960 --> 00:45:50,420
[SPEAKER_01] to možda može doći kasnije.

1113
00:45:50,420 --> 00:45:52,019
[SPEAKER_01] Ali mislim da ono,

1114
00:45:52,019 --> 00:45:54,619
[SPEAKER_01] naučit slušat taj svoj

1115
00:45:54,619 --> 00:45:56,579
[SPEAKER_01] i dat mu kredibilitet.

1116
00:45:56,579 --> 00:45:57,559
[SPEAKER_01] Ono, okej, ne želim,

1117
00:45:57,559 --> 00:45:58,980
[SPEAKER_01] pa možda ću ono,

1118
00:45:58,980 --> 00:46:00,780
[SPEAKER_01] ili ću reći ne ide mi se,

1119
00:46:00,780 --> 00:46:02,679
[SPEAKER_01] ili ću sad pa promisli zaš mi se ne ide.

1120
00:46:02,760 --> 00:46:04,119
[SPEAKER_01] ili ću svjesno onda oteći,

1121
00:46:04,119 --> 00:46:05,519
[SPEAKER_01] pa vidi ti me to dovede.

1122
00:46:05,519 --> 00:46:08,639
[SPEAKER_01] Ali ja iskreno mislim da

1123
00:46:08,639 --> 00:46:12,300
[SPEAKER_01] svi mi u tom trenutku,

1124
00:46:12,300 --> 00:46:13,559
[SPEAKER_01] recimo agreeable,

1125
00:46:13,559 --> 00:46:15,139
[SPEAKER_01] kad kažeš da,

1126
00:46:15,139 --> 00:46:16,539
[SPEAKER_01] možda želiš reći ne,

1127
00:46:16,539 --> 00:46:17,619
[SPEAKER_01] ili kasnije misliš,

1128
00:46:17,619 --> 00:46:18,980
[SPEAKER_01] osjetiš ti to,

1129
00:46:18,980 --> 00:46:21,019
[SPEAKER_01] osjetiš da pristaješ na nešto

1130
00:46:21,019 --> 00:46:21,719
[SPEAKER_01] što nije

1131
00:46:21,719 --> 00:46:24,280
[SPEAKER_01] uravnoteženo možda s tobom.

1132
00:46:25,099 --> 00:46:27,659
[SPEAKER_01] Ali neki ljudi su naučili

1133
00:46:27,659 --> 00:46:29,639
[SPEAKER_01] tako se adaptirat,

1134
00:46:29,639 --> 00:46:31,199
[SPEAKER_01] jer, kažem opet,

1135
00:46:31,199 --> 00:46:35,239
[SPEAKER_01] svako je neki drugi put prolazio.

1136
00:46:35,239 --> 00:46:36,260
[SPEAKER_01] Neko je ko djete,

1137
00:46:36,260 --> 00:46:37,300
[SPEAKER_01] ne znam,

1138
00:46:37,300 --> 00:46:39,840
[SPEAKER_01] pokušavao se zauzeti za sebe,

1139
00:46:39,840 --> 00:46:41,079
[SPEAKER_01] pa je na jedan ili na drugi način

1140
00:46:41,079 --> 00:46:41,659
[SPEAKER_01] bio kažnjen.

1141
00:46:41,659 --> 00:46:42,519
[SPEAKER_01] Možda je od društva,

1142
00:46:42,519 --> 00:46:43,780
[SPEAKER_01] možda je došlo pa je rekao

