[SPEAKER_01] Znaš, kod da nisam

1770
01:13:24,460 --> 01:13:26,960
[SPEAKER_01] kod da nisam mogo skužiti

1771
01:13:26,960 --> 01:13:29,300
[SPEAKER_01] ko je slaven ako to se maknem.

1772
01:13:29,300 --> 01:13:31,340
[SPEAKER_01] Ali moj osobni put

1773
