[SPEAKER_01] i to si rekla na početku

1777
01:13:40,359 --> 01:13:41,720
[SPEAKER_01] ima jako puno variabli.

1778
01:13:41,720 --> 01:13:44,279
[SPEAKER_01] I ti ne možeš ništa od toga

1779
01:13:44,279 --> 01:13:45,359
[SPEAKER_01] realno kontrolirati.

1780
01:13:45,359 --> 01:13:47,380
[SPEAKER_01] Jer ti sve, sve utječe na tebe

1781
01:13:47,380 --> 01:13:48,500
[SPEAKER_01] i okolina.

1782
01:13:48,500 --> 01:13:50,680
[SPEAKER_01] Mislim, okolina sve spada pod okolinu.

1783
01:13:50,680 --> 01:13:52,579
[SPEAKER_01] Ali ti da i tvoje traume

1784
01:13:52,579 --> 01:13:53,600
[SPEAKER_01] ali i genetika

1785
01:13:53,600 --> 01:13:55,539
