1805
01:14:28,420 --> 01:14:30,020
[SPEAKER_01] To isto utječe na tebe.

1806
01:14:30,020 --> 01:14:32,199
[SPEAKER_01] Ali nije ta genetika stvorila

1807
01:14:32,199 --> 01:14:35,000
