1808
01:14:35,000 --> 01:14:36,340
[SPEAKER_01] Nego je genetika

1809
01:14:36,340 --> 01:14:37,619
[SPEAKER_01] jedan od ono

1810
01:14:37,619 --> 01:14:40,119
[SPEAKER_01] tih začina u tom životu

1811
01:14:40,119 --> 01:14:41,060
[SPEAKER_01] koji na kraju čini

1812
01:14:41,060 --> 01:14:43,840
