1826
01:15:00,760 --> 01:15:03,439
[SPEAKER_01] To je meni bilo super.

1827
01:15:03,439 --> 01:15:05,180
[SPEAKER_01] U jednom trenutku si osvijesti

1828
01:15:05,180 --> 01:15:05,619
[SPEAKER_01] da ono,

1829
01:15:05,619 --> 01:15:06,939
[SPEAKER_01] nije bitno,

1830
