1848
01:15:30,779 --> 01:15:31,760
[SPEAKER_01] bio bi neko drugi.

1849
01:15:31,760 --> 01:15:33,539
[SPEAKER_01] Apsolutno.

1850
01:15:33,539 --> 01:15:34,720
[SPEAKER_01] Da li je to pravi,

1851
