1857
01:15:39,939 --> 01:15:41,520
[SPEAKER_01] i on je najpraviji trenutno.

1858
01:15:41,520 --> 01:15:43,279
[SPEAKER_01] On je prošao sve to

1859
01:15:43,279 --> 01:15:45,659
[SPEAKER_01] i je ok s time.

1860
01:15:45,659 --> 01:15:46,899
[SPEAKER_01] I doće nešto drugo

