[SPEAKER_01] Dosta je to filozofske,

1886
01:16:19,859 --> 01:16:20,680
[SPEAKER_01] opet sve orijentirano,

1887
01:16:20,680 --> 01:16:22,119
[SPEAKER_01] dosta je to moj osobni put,

1888
