01:58:10,399 --> 01:58:11,100
[SPEAKER_00] idemo tamo,

3367
01:58:11,100 --> 01:58:11,399
[SPEAKER_00] znaš.

3368
01:58:11,399 --> 01:58:13,680
[SPEAKER_00] Stalo sam bio okružen nekim ljudima.

3369
01:58:14,100 --> 01:58:19,039
[SPEAKER_00] I koliko god,

3370
01:58:19,039 --> 01:58:20,899
[SPEAKER_00] ono,

3371
01:58:20,899 --> 01:58:24,479
[SPEAKER_00] se možda nekaj činilo da nevamo mi nikakvog utjecaja i kontrole,

3372
01:58:24,479 --> 01:58:28,960
[SPEAKER_00] ja kad god sam se u životu zaintačio,

3373
01:58:28,960 --> 01:58:29,699
[SPEAKER_00] kad bi ono rekli,

3374
01:58:29,699 --> 01:58:30,000
[SPEAKER_00] ono,

3375
01:58:30,000 --> 01:58:30,279
[SPEAKER_00] naš,

3376
01:58:30,279 --> 01:58:30,960
[SPEAKER_00] brute force,

3377
01:58:30,960 --> 01:58:31,220
[SPEAKER_00] ono,

3378
01:58:31,220 --> 01:58:34,180
[SPEAKER_00] kako bi preveli brute force?

3379
01:58:35,239 --> 01:58:35,460
[SPEAKER_00] Ono,

3380
01:58:35,460 --> 01:58:36,659
[SPEAKER_00] velik, velik,

3381
01:58:36,659 --> 01:58:37,000
[SPEAKER_00] znači,

3382
01:58:37,000 --> 01:58:37,920
[SPEAKER_00] surovom silom.

3383
01:58:37,920 --> 01:58:42,680
[SPEAKER_00] Surovom silom ču ja pretvoriti to u svoju realnost.

3384
01:58:42,680 --> 01:58:43,479
[SPEAKER_01] Da, da.

3385
01:58:43,479 --> 01:58:47,500
[SPEAKER_00] Skužio sam da kad mi je takav stav,

3386
01:58:47,500 --> 01:58:52,739
[SPEAKER_00] da imam više šanse da se to stvarno realizira.

3387
01:58:52,739 --> 01:58:54,899
[SPEAKER_00] Ono što želim, jel?

3388
01:58:54,899 --> 01:58:59,039
[SPEAKER_00] Ne mora, ali osjećam da imam više šanse.

3389
01:58:59,039 --> 01:59:01,199
[SPEAKER_00] Čak ono što mi je smiješno, nekad,

3390
01:59:01,199 --> 01:59:04,520
[SPEAKER_00] mislim da ako više brinemo nećemo da imam više šanse

3391
01:59:04,520 --> 01:59:05,619
[SPEAKER_00] da će se realizirati.

3392
01:59:05,619 --> 01:59:07,859
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, kao bio sam preopušten oko toga

3393
01:59:07,859 --> 01:59:09,359
[SPEAKER_00] i kao,

3394
01:59:09,359 --> 01:59:11,680
[SPEAKER_00] jebiga, vidiš, nije se realizirao,

3395
01:59:11,680 --> 01:59:11,859
[SPEAKER_00] znači,

3396
01:59:11,859 --> 01:59:12,760
[SPEAKER_00] da sam bio preopušten.

3397
01:59:12,760 --> 01:59:13,420
[SPEAKER_01] Da, da.

3398
01:59:13,420 --> 01:59:15,239
[SPEAKER_00] Možda da sam se malo više brinu,

3399
01:59:15,239 --> 01:59:16,520
[SPEAKER_00] možda bi nešto više napravio.

3400
01:59:16,520 --> 01:59:18,479
[SPEAKER_01] Ja vjerujem da je to istina.

3401
01:59:18,479 --> 01:59:21,180
[SPEAKER_00] Ono, da li je sad ono život kao,

3402
01:59:21,180 --> 01:59:22,899
[SPEAKER_00] to list na vjetru, sreća,

3403
01:59:22,899 --> 01:59:24,159
[SPEAKER_00] ono.

3404
01:59:24,159 --> 01:59:24,979
[SPEAKER_01] Pa sve.

3405
01:59:24,979 --> 01:59:26,939
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam na tih 51 posta.

3406
01:59:26,939 --> 01:59:28,420
[SPEAKER_01] Meni je to 51,49.

3407
01:59:28,420 --> 01:59:33,699
[SPEAKER_01] Da.

3408
01:59:33,800 --> 01:59:40,140
[SPEAKER_01] Nisam bacio si me u razmišljanje.

3409
01:59:40,140 --> 01:59:42,220
[SPEAKER_00] Kako je to bio ovaj, neki tvoji?

3410
01:59:42,220 --> 01:59:42,960
[SPEAKER_00] Bio stric.

3411
01:59:42,960 --> 01:59:44,220
[SPEAKER_01] Stric, stric.

3412
01:59:44,220 --> 01:59:47,779
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, to mi je ostalo od tebe u pamćinju.

3413
01:59:47,779 --> 01:59:49,720
[SPEAKER_00] Kad se nastane, nastane neki tajac.

3414
01:59:50,460 --> 01:59:52,880
[SPEAKER_00] Kad ti stari ljudi kažu, ja.

3415
01:59:52,880 --> 01:59:56,300
[SPEAKER_01] To je to, to je to samo da prekino.

3416
01:59:56,800 --> 02:00:06,439
[SPEAKER_01] Ne, ne, ne, pa bacio si me ono, kad ja sam malo ono baš tako razmišljati u svojoj glavi o tome što si govorio.

3417
02:00:07,560 --> 02:00:19,520
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, ne znam, nismo neku mašnicu zavezali za kraj našeg razgovora, ali dragom je da si ti bio prvi gost u mom novom studiju.

3418
02:00:19,819 --> 02:00:21,279
[SPEAKER_01] Najbolji koji sam ja do sad vidio.

3419
02:00:21,279 --> 02:00:22,020
[SPEAKER_00] Studiju.

3420
02:00:22,020 --> 02:00:22,880
[SPEAKER_00] Da.

3421
02:00:22,880 --> 02:00:25,199
[SPEAKER_01] Jer sam bio u onom starom, starom, tako da.

3422
02:00:25,199 --> 02:00:25,819
[SPEAKER_01] Aha, da, da.

3423
02:00:25,819 --> 02:00:26,960
[SPEAKER_01] E, nisam ih sve prošao.

3424
02:00:26,960 --> 02:00:27,560
[SPEAKER_01] Najbolji moji.

3425
02:00:27,560 --> 02:00:28,819
[SPEAKER_01] Da, da, da.

3426
02:00:28,819 --> 02:00:54,039
[SPEAKER_00] I, evo, kako nekako obita, prvo ti se želim zahvaliti na tome, moje iskustvo do sadašnje, každa ću o bit ljudima vrijedna, epizoda je vrijedan razgovor, mislim da smo baš ono, uletili u, ja sam zaborio i da, u trenucijmi da snimamo i da ovo, da ono, baš smo lijepo razgovarali, meni je bilo ugodno baš.

3427
02:00:54,699 --> 02:01:16,180
[SPEAKER_01] Meni isto, meni isto, i čak, mislim da je bitno, znaš, o pocijetit se, švi mi, znaš, kako se rekao, znamo sve, treba se znat, sjetit, ono, i baš i stvari u ovom razgovoru su me pocijetila neke i moje misli i tvoja pitanja, no, promislito nečemu tako da, mislim da je to isto bitno, uvijek treba držati taj nekakav.

3428
02:01:16,180 --> 02:01:42,460
[SPEAKER_01] Pa, to neko gledalo, naš, ono, da se propitaš, da te nešto izazove, da promisliš, jer tu kontrolu imaš, ono, pa, ta hvala tebi na tome, evo i na tim pitanjima i na diskusiji, na razgovoru i na neukazanom povjerenju jutros i ukazanom povjerenju nakon toga i, da.

3429
02:01:43,180 --> 02:01:57,039
[SPEAKER_00] Ekipa, nadam se da ste uživali, isto kao ja, vidimo se za cijan dana, pretplati se, zaprati nas tamo negdje, na tim bespućima interneta.

3430
02:01:57,039 --> 02:01:58,319
[SPEAKER_01] E, jedni mod.

3431
02:01:58,319 --> 02:01:59,699
[SPEAKER_00] Vidimo se, bok.

3432
02:01:59,699 --> 02:02:00,220
[SPEAKER_01] Pozdrav.

